India get past the 300 mark thanks to contributions from Shreyas, Sanju and Washington's amazing finish. Not to forget the amazing start provided by Dhawan and Gill. It will be very exciting to see the likes of Arshdeep and Umran Malik who are making their debut today and how they will approach the challenge ahead of them. Will the Indian bowling be able defend this score or will the New Zealand batters help them get over the line? Lets's wait and watch
